# Trade Finance System - Hyperledger Fabric

A comprehensive blockchain-based trade finance system implementing Letter of Credit (LC) functionality on Hyperledger Fabric.
This enterprise-grade solution demonstrates real-world trade finance workflows with multi-organizational participation,
complex endorsement policies, and integration patterns for traditional banking systems.

## üéØ Project Overview

This project showcases a production-ready trade finance platform built on Hyperledger Fabric 2.3+, designed to digitize and 
streamline Letter of Credit operations across multiple financial institutions, shipping companies, and regulatory bodies.
The system eliminates paper-based processes, reduces processing time, and provides transparency across all stakeholders.

### Key Business Flows

- **LC Issuance**: Applicant requests LC, issuing bank creates and submits to advising bank
- **LC Acceptance**: Beneficiary reviews and accepts LC terms
- **Shipping**: Goods are shipped after LC acceptance provides payment guarantee
- **Document Submission**: Beneficiary submits shipping documents for verification.
- **Rest of the flow can implementated 

