## üìù Development Notes

### Key Design Decisions

**Shared Identities vs Individual Identities**
- System uses shared blockchain identities per organization
- API layer maps individual users to organization identity
- Reduces wallet management complexity
- Enables efficient multi-tenant operations

**Business Logic Sequencing**
- LC acceptance occurs before shipping (provides payment guarantee)
- Document verification requires both banks
- Payment release only after successful verification chain

**Certificate Management**
- Certificates regenerate on network restart
- Connection profiles must be regenerated
- Automated scripts reduce manual intervention

